  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to dnsmasq</title>

    <para>
    <application>dnsmasq</application> is a lightweight, easy-to-configure DNS forwarder and DHCP server. It is designed to provide network services to small-scale networks, such as home or office setups, and is commonly used in embedded systems and containerized environments.
    </para>

